{"tid":342244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(花生) 幼稚園簽完約改口話唔駛咁多老師","createTime":"2017-07-31T12:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T13:56:36.000Z","uid":49208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09ed38acfb1142d03b71e23cc56c9a64f0fd1cdc","tid":342244,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"fb見到轉過黎：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/TeacherVoice/posts/1415564361861115?comment_id=1415581045192780\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTeacherVoice%2Fposts%2F1415564361861115%3Fcomment_id%3D1415581045192780&h=b61398e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TeacherVoice/posts/1415564361861115?comment_id=1415581045192780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTeacherVoice%2Fposts%2F1415564361861115%3Fcomment_id%3D1415581045192780&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c3e0057b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TeacherVoice/posts/1415564361861115?comment_id=1415581045192780</a><br />\n<br />\n#1708268<br />\n&quot;我真係好唔開心...但好長篇...<br />\n話說年頭個陣有間幼稚園請左我做音樂老師，人工二萬幾，全職黎。簽好哂約八月開工。咁我好開心地辭左本身份工，仲報埋外國一年個啲pgde 好好準備份新工。<br />\n<br />\n點知七月頭，校董搵我，叫左我入房，話突然發現唔駛咁多老師，拿住張新約叫我轉part time ,由music teacher 變normal teacher ,兩年約變一年約。人工減一半。我話可唔可以諗下？因為人工減一半我真係接受唔到同維持唔到生活，佢話，<span style=\"color: red;\">「都既成事實啦，有咩好唔簽」</span>當時喊哂咁堅持要走，後尾我走到。<br />\n我一踏出校門我勁徬徨，本身份工又辭左，而家突然話轉part time。咁我就打返去問個主任，如果我堅持唔簽會點，佢地一直比唔到答案我，只係不停游說叫我簽，同埋用我pgde 需要mentor 黎要脅我。我就睇返我地張舊約，入邊有條terms 係<span style=\"color: red;\">「如果是但一方响合約生效前想毁約，咁要六個月通知或者賠十萬」</span>。<br />\n同一時間我都有搵工，好好彩比我好快搵到另一份。咁我就問本身間學校，我話其實你只係想要part time 咁不如大家和平解約啦？但佢地可能怕我事後話佢地毁約（因為舊約埋份不公平嘅新約都响我手）所以佢地唔肯，仲立即話比我做返full time 。但講真，就算做返好明顯我日子都唔會好過。咁而家我唯一一條路就係一返到去立即resign 。<br />\n問題又黎，合約寫左响試用期頭三個月，辭職要十四日通知。但我打過去勞工署，佢話根據勞工法57條，試用期第一個月內係可以即走。無論合約點寫都好，响第一個月裡邊，勞工法都會凌駕合約。<br />\n有無人可以話我知係咪咖？因為呢件事我真係好stressed 😭😭😭😭😭😭😭😭&quot;<br />\n---<br />\n留言: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1LdnAkC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1LdnAkC&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=18af55a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1LdnAkC</a><br />\n服務: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1ZFpxjk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1ZFpxjk&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=80eae290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1ZFpxjk</a><br />\n培養學生抗逆能力: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pqKjCJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pqKjCJ&d=49yC84XGkIvLbS4T9B%2FwoJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=05d07774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pqKjCJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「都既成事實啦，有咩好唔簽」呢句真係金句，個格同香港政府一撚樣"},{"pid":"d9c4a009d3e7a75b8671ded0f89cf68f22e8e997","tid":342244,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"&quot;有得袋住先, 真係唔要? &quot;"},{"pid":"42f649fc72f541d89167ffff96e91a42f0553091","tid":342244,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"做咩唔叫佢賠10萬"},{"pid":"2874e72efcfe370a79d5e5d4c48e2875c74cebd2","tid":342244,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"做乜唔告違約"},{"pid":"b93d2a30ae3199ec7426a8d833d4ce1c00a6ba04","tid":342244,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"987bbd4eeaf31abc1df069c0125fe88ab5935507","tid":342244,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩唔叫佢賠10萬</blockquote><br />\n到時佢就會同你講試用期內可以即走。<br />\n教育界好多人用啲完全唔make sense嘅廢話理由呃fresh grad搏你乜都唔識"},{"pid":"85633f48f8c5dd0d407778661f0ce73656acf10d","tid":342244,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"一個月會即走"},{"pid":"6e05e7dc798df2a3ef0a4bb1c627e9546aecaa3a","tid":342244,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做咩唔叫佢賠10萬</blockquote><br />\n到時佢就會同你講試用期內可以即走。<br />\n教育界好多人用啲完全唔make sense嘅廢話理由呃fresh grad搏你乜都唔識</blockquote><br />\n係囉， mentor 理由都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}